						<summary>

						<p>Threshold slab of the goddess's shrine of the Bhairava temple.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record the obeisance of some devotees whose images are embossed in flat relief in the act of prostrating before the god. Mentions Tatvaprakāśa-Yōgi. In late characters.</p>						

